&lt;h2 id="removing-unused-packages" class=link_owner&gt;
 Removing unused packages
 &lt;a href="#removing-unused-packages" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
